XfamObject module¶

class XfamObject.XfamObject(name, db, type_)¶

Bases: object

An abstract class, base for PfamFamily,PfamClan,RfamFamily and RfamClan.

get_tree()¶

Get phylogenetic tree of entry if entry is not a clan. :return: Phylogenetic tree in newick format :rettype: Bio.Phylo.Newick.Tree
